name: The Secretist
description:
The Secretist is the ultimate source of knowledge within the Tapestry.
Both collector and purveyor of secrets, He answers to those who call for him and reveals the secret truths of the universe.
In exchange, all He asks is for the dreamer to relinquish some knowledge of his own, no matter how mundane it might be.
Such a deal might seem fair, but, beware, to be exposed to secret knowledge and expose oneself in turn always carries dire consequences and He who dwells in secrets knows it better than anyone else.
